                <div class="view view-property-articles-by-og view-id-property_articles_by_og view-display-id-block_2 view-dom-id-ea209c34a907119175f9d1739e29c145">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
      

<div id="views-bootstrap-grid-1" class="views-bootstrap-grid-plugin-style">
  
          <div class="row">
                  <div class=" col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
              
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-image">        <div class="field-content"><a href="/en/un-chronicle/realistic-goal-culture-sustainable-development-agenda"><img typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-responsive" src="https://www.un.org/sites/un2.un.org/files/styles/large-article-image-style-16-9/public/field/image/2025/11/adobestock_382725021_barcelona_spain.png" alt="Barcelona, Spain. Credit: Adobe Stock " title="A view of Barcelona, Spain, site of the 2025 UNESCO World Conference on Cultural Policies and Sustainable Development, known as MONDIACULT. Adobe Stock " /></a></div>  </div>  
  <div>        <div class="category">Stephen Wyber</div>  </div>  
  <div>        <h3><a href="/en/un-chronicle/realistic-goal-culture-sustainable-development-agenda">A Realistic Goal? Culture in the Sustainable Development Agenda</a></h3>  </div>  
  <div>        <div class="summary"><p>Far from being restricted to those Sustainable Development Goals&nbsp;that explicitly touch on culture, governments are highlighting connections to culture across the 2030 Agenda.</p>
</div>  </div>          </div>

                                      <div class=" col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
              
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-image">        <div class="field-content"><a href="/en/un-chronicle/diabetes-across-life-stages-growing-global-challenge-0"><img typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-responsive" src="https://www.un.org/sites/un2.un.org/files/styles/large-article-image-style-16-9/public/field/image/2025/11/diabetes_in_india_2016_1.jpg?c=0c7e2a0eaed56628d23c097c25d9b627" alt="Diabetes patients exercising early in the morning in a public space in Mumbai, India. WHO" title="Diabetes patients exercising early in the morning in a public space in Mumbai, India. WHO / Atul Loke, Panos Pictures" /></a></div>  </div>  
  <div>        <div class="category">Bianca Hemmingsen, Sanjana Marpadga and Alarcos Cieza</div>  </div>  
  <div>        <h3><a href="/en/un-chronicle/diabetes-across-life-stages-growing-global-challenge-0">Diabetes across Life Stages: A Growing Global Challenge</a></h3>  </div>  
  <div>        <div class="summary"><p>A life-course approach is foundational for implementation of the World Health Organization&nbsp;Global Diabetes Compact. Every stage of life presents unique risks, needs and opportunities for intervention.</p>
</div>  </div>          </div>

                                                                                                                <div class=" col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
              
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-image">        <div class="field-content"><a href="/en/un-chronicle/rebuilding-trust-multilateral-governance-lessons-seabed-cop-30"><img typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-responsive" src="https://www.un.org/sites/un2.un.org/files/styles/large-article-image-style-16-9/public/field/image/2025/11/octopus_on_seabed_in_hudson_canyon_0.png" alt="A deep-sea octopus on the seabead in Hudson Canyon, located off the Atlantic Coast of the United States. National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Office of Ocean (NOAA) Exploration and Research" title="A deep-sea octopus on the seabed in the Hudson Canyon, located off the Atlantic coast of the United States. Credit: National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) Office of Ocean Exploration and Research" /></a></div>  </div>  
  <div>        <div class="category">Carlos Garca-Soto</div>  </div>  
  <div>        <h3><a href="/en/un-chronicle/rebuilding-trust-multilateral-governance-lessons-seabed-cop-30">Rebuilding Trust in Multilateral Governance: Lessons from the Seabed to COP 30</a></h3>  </div>  
  <div>        <div class="summary"><p>Whether on climate, biodiversity or the deep ocean, public confidence in how global institutions make decisions has become as important as the decisions themselves.</p>
</div>  </div>          </div>

